text:
kya likhun? or kahan se suru kru bhai? 
Avoid kr rha tha abhi tak likhna but mera memoir k bina tumhre yearbook page acha ni lgega na ğŸ¥º
First time mila tha na tb lga ki ye bandi bat hi nhi krti kese rahunga iske sath but mrko thodi pta tha ki ye bandi , ye meri iitk vli maa h xD. First year m esc lab jana tumhra n merse "all the best" mangna.. bro, dar or proud vli feel ek sath ati thi, dar ki all the best kam kr jaye, and proud isly ki mera all the best kitna matter krta h tumhre liy....Ek tum hi ho jiske sath campus ka har ek din kata h mera.... Mere liy ghar se khane k saman lana, mithayi lana, or kya kuch...Har fest k phle merko kapde select krke dena ki ye pehen lo kyuki merko to kuch samaj ata hi nhi tha, ghar p maa btati h ye kapde pehen lo, campus m tum ya sakshi xD. Fir second year mein tumhre sath tumhre mama k ghar nikal jana kitna mast tha vo bhi , and yeah sab tumhre hath k khane k liy tarste hein but us din mne atleast cake khaya tha kaafi tasty tha, itna ki mene do teen baar liya tha kitchen m jakar...Campus k har kand mein mera sath dena, kyuki kand to ho hi jata tha but pta tha abha n bhai h sambhal lenge. Har din tumhre room m time pass krna,tumhe pareshan krna, tumhre age faltu cheezo k liy rona...kita miss krta hun yaar mein and exam k bad kuch to tv series dekhna n beech m discuss krna ki ye possibility ho skti h, esa ho skta h n next episode m check krna ki apna prediction kitne sahi h...late night canteen jana....Aunty ko jabrdasti campus bulana or fir unke sath campus ghumna was ğŸ’.
ese to bahut kuch h likhne ko kya kya likhun ğŸ¥±
Campus life tumhre sath hi suru hui and tumhre sath hi khatam ho rhi h...merko cycle p acads area tak leke jana, sath m gym jana, fest mein jana, room p beth k campus ki hazaro bate discuss krna, har decision m ek dusre se puchna, mess sath jane k liy ek dusre k wait krna kabhi tumhri CS ki meeting, kabhi meri SPO ki but fir bhi wait krte the bhale hi mess k khana chut jaye but khynge sath mein....
Tumhre jesa selfish sayd hi life mein koi aya h meri, aa jao hyd aage ki jindgi bhi asaan ho jygi and fashion illustration k kaam suru krte hein tbtk mein thoda bahut skill sheekta ghar p , or thoda to mujhme phle se h hi ğŸ˜›

Chlo baaki to diary page p likha h, vo milne aaoge to dikhunga....
